==Entrances & Exits==
===Entrances===
Entrances to '''Level 321''' remain various, without a consistent threshold or a specific method to enter. Although there’s a probable correlation between entry to '''Level 321''' through hotel levels due to internal similarities, one is more likely to come through transitional halls with lavender themes. The earliest example of this has been recorded on [[Level 5|<span style="color:white;background:linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(225, 30, 30, 1), rgba(75, 15, 15, 1)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">Terror Hotel</span>]]’s halls.
===Exits===
Exits vary through '''Level 321''', and most of them are difficult or seldom, tho consistent methods are listed below:

*Some fields throughout within The Outside might transition into [[Level 660|<span style="font-family:Instrument Serif;color:white;background:linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(86, 40, 166, 1), rgba(40, 12, 88, 1)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">MANDRAKE MORTALITY</span>]] on occasions, so far this is the most common way to exit '''Level 321'''.
*Wandering too deep into the rural parts of The Outside with persistent progress may lead one into [[Level 500|<span style="text-shadow: 1px 1px 10px #FFFFFF69;background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 97, 97, 1), rgba(173, 255, 179, 1), rgba(173, 174, 255, 1)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">'''Aurora Corealis'''</span>]], though this method is highly dangerous and unworthy.
*Rarely, halls within the interior of '''Level 321''' may contain thresholds to [[Level 403|<span style="color:rgb(200, 200, 200);">ERROR 403 FORBIDDEN</span>]], yet most of these tresholds appear as regular accomodation entries and often goes unnoticed.
*On exceptional occasions, salons may contain a passage to [[Level 88|<span style="color:white;background:linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(30, 130, 166, 1), rgba(40, 70, 88, 1)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">'''Atlantis' Aquarius Dining'''</span>]].
*More constant exits are yet to be discovered.

